      #productsandservices
        h2 Products and Services
        .line
        .service
          div
            h3 Games development
            p We consider ourselves a entrepreneur company. And game development is one of our main goals.
            p GnA is a new company formed by experienced people in different areas of the software world, one of the areas is the creation of video games. Our experience is based in multimedia and entertainment software projects that gave us the experience to start producing games in the video game market.
          img(src='images/game.png')
        .service
          div
            h3 Mobile apps
            p The world is changing and so the way to do business. Now there are more mobile devices than computers in the world. This is the reason that mobile development is one of our main purposes.
            p We have the expertice and the knowledge to build apps for any device out there, because if we haven't done it yet, we will.
          img(src='images/apps.png')
        .service
          div
            h3 Software as a Service
            p We are good at using our creativity and knowledge to build great cloud solutions for our customers.
            p We also believe that cloud computing is the future way to do business. And we are doing it now.
            p Having our own services out there is an advantage that give our customers the confidence they need.
          img(src='images/sas.png')
      #aboutus
        h2 More about Us
        .line
        p We have more than 10 years of experience in software development and a huge background in business.
        p GnA started in 2012 as a mobile apps provider for some companies, soon the love for video games and entertainment begin to open the right doors for us. Now games and applications are our main area of business.
        p Our team is composed by a group of young people, developers, designers and artists. Together we can create and give life to new ideas and project that will someday turn us one of the biggest software creators in the world.
        #logos
          img.html5(src='images/html5.png')
          img.css3(src='images/css3.png')
          img.javascript(src='images/javascript.png')
          img.ios(src='images/ios.png')
          img.java(src='images/java.png')
          img.dotnet(src='images/dotnet.png')
        p We can assure you the amount of knowledge in GnA will grow every day!
      #contact
        h2 Contact us and let us know how we can help you
        .line
        aside
          p Learn more from us in the social media links.
          img(src='images/LinkedIn.png')
          img(src='images/twitter.png')
          a(href='https://www.facebook.com/gnastudio', target='_blank')
            img(src='images/facebook.png').fb
        form(method='POST', action='/contact')#form
          input#name(type='text', placeholder='Name', required, name='contact[name]')
          input#email(type='email', placeholder='Email', required, name='contact[email]')
          input#company(type='text', placeholder='Company', required, name='contact[company]')
          textarea#message(rows='4', placeholder='Message', required, name='contact[message]')
          input(type='submit', value='Send')
          p#servermessage
        .clearfix
